# Sample HTTP requests — exercises the REST client (rest.nvim / kulala.nvim)
# and treesitter highlight. Run the request under the cursor with the buffer's
# REST keymap (see the REST guide / cheatsheet).

### Simple GET
GET https://httpbin.org/get
Accept: application/json

### GET with query parameters
GET https://httpbin.org/get?editor=neovim&feature=rest
Accept: application/json

### POST with a JSON body
POST https://httpbin.org/post
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "arcane-centaur",
  "editor": "neovim",
  "features": ["lsp", "treesitter", "repl"]
}

### Custom headers
GET https://httpbin.org/headers
Accept: application/json
X-Sample-Header: test-value
